  "about_app": "The \"Holy Quran - Hikma Library\" app is an integrated application that offers a wide range of features to enhance the experience of reading and learning the Holy Quran, including:",
  "@about_app": {
    "type": "text",
    "placeholders": {}
  },
  "about_app2": "Among the most important features of the application :",
  "@about_app2": {
    "type": "text",
    "placeholders": {}
  },
  "about_app3": "۞ A modern, easy-to-use interface: A contemporary, intuitive design that makes it easy to navigate and access all features, with a new calendar view and the ability to browse the full yearly calendar.\n۞ Adopting the King Fahd Complex edition: The app relies on the King Fahd Complex Mushaf edition, known for its accuracy and reliability.\n۞ Interactive, comprehensive reading: A flexible reading experience in either Mushaf-page mode or single-ayah mode, with full interaction with the text.\n۞ Advanced listening: Listen to ayahs and surahs with voices of selected reciters, with the feature of showing the current ayahs during playback, plus the ability to listen to each word separately to enhance learning.\n۞ Fast search and navigation: Instant search within Qur'an verses with direct jump to the desired surah or page, and smooth navigation between surahs.\n۞ Tafsir and Islamic library: Access a collection of tafsir and translations, in addition to an integrated Islamic library that includes Hadith and tafsir books.\n۞ Tajweed and its rules: Clear display of tajweed and its rules, with the addition of the Ten Qira'at to broaden understanding of recitation methods.\n۞ Advanced linguistic analysis: Display morphology (tasreef) and i'rab for each word, helping deeper understanding of linguistic meanings in the Qur'an.\n۞ Similar verses: A dedicated feature to display similar verses to make memorization and review easier.\n۞ Reading and memorization management: Add bookmarks for ayahs and pages to return to them anytime.\n۞ Reading stop signs: Clarify waqf signs to help users read correctly.\n۞ Hisn Al-Muslim adhkar: A complete section for reading adhkar with favorites and quick navigation between sections.\n۞ Display customization: Support changing color styles, including dark mode, for a comfortable reading experience.\n۞ Downloading and offline use: Download surahs and listen later without an internet connection.\n\nThese features make the \"Holy Quran - Hikma Library\" app an integrated platform combining reading, listening, tafsir, and learning, offering a rich and easy-to-use spiritual and educational experience.",
